## 1. Foundation Phase

### Decision Tree

```mermaid
flowchart TD
    A[Start New Project] --> B{Type of Application?}
    B -->|Web App| C[Continue]
    B -->|Mobile| D[Consider React Native or Flutter]
    B -->|API Only| E[Skip UI steps]
    C --> F{Have Existing Backend?}
    F -->|Yes| G[Connect to Existing API]
    F -->|No| H[Choose Backend Strategy]
```

### Always Do First

1. **Initialize repository:**

   ```bash
   # Create directory and init git
   mkdir my-project && cd my-project
   git init

   # Create initial commit
   echo "# My Project" > README.md
   git add -A && git commit -m "Initial commit"
   ```

2. **Choose package manager:**
   | Manager | Best For | Install |
   |---------|----------|---------|
   | pnpm | Production apps, monorepos | `npm install -g pnpm` |
   | npm | Universal compatibility | Comes with Node.js |
   | yarn | Legacy projects | `npm install -g yarn` |
   | bun | Speed critical, experimental | `curl -fsSL https://bun.sh/install` |

3. **Create .gitignore:**

   ```
   # Dependencies
   node_modules/

   # Environment
   .env
   .env.local

   # Build output
   dist/
   build/
   .next/

   # IDE
   .vscode/
   .idea/

   # OS
   .DS_Store
   Thumbs.db

   # Logs
   *.log
   npm-debug.log*
   ```

