## 6. Styling & UI

### Decision Tree

```mermaid
flowchart TD
    A[Styling] --> B{Team Experience?}
    B -->|Tailwind| C[Tailwind CSS]
    B -->|CSS Modules| D[CSS Modules]
    B -->|Styled Components| E[Styled Components]
    C --> F{Need UI Library?}
    F -->|Yes| G[Shadcn/ui or Radix]
    F -->|No| H[Custom Components]
```

### Styling Options

| Approach              | Use When                                      | Skip When                             |
| --------------------- | --------------------------------------------- | ------------------------------------- |
| **Tailwind CSS**      | Rapid development, team knows utility classes | Strong preference against utility CSS |
| **CSS Modules**       | Scoped styling, no build config               | Need theming                          |
| **Styled Components** | Component encapsulation                       | SSR complexity concerns               |
| **Vanilla CSS**       | Very simple projects                          | Maintainability                       |

