```

### Language Conventions

| Region               | Use For                                         | Example                   |
| -------------------- | ----------------------------------------------- | ------------------------- |
| **British English**  | UK, Australia, South Africa, user-facing labels | colour, programme, centre |
| **American English** | US, code, technical docs                        | color, program, center    |

### Code vs User-Facing

| Context            | Language             | Notes                   |
| ------------------ | -------------------- | ----------------------- |
| **Code/Variables** | Standard conventions | Follow library docs     |
| **Config files**   | Standard conventions | Don't break tooling     |
| **Comments**       | Team preference      | Keep consistent         |
| **UI Labels**      | User region          | Match user expectations |
| **AI Prompts**     | As required          | May differ from UI      |

